      <title>MarkDown_Basic03</title>
      <link href="/2022/10/10/MarkDown_Basic03/"/>
      <url>/2022/10/10/MarkDown_Basic03/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><font size="6"><b>This is a series of codes for learning MarkDown Grammar.</b></font></p><h2 id="内嵌-HTML-标签"><strong>内嵌 HTML 标签</strong></h2><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">This <span class="strong">**word**</span> is bold. This <span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">em</span>&gt;</span></span>word<span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">em</span>&gt;</span></span> is italic.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>This <strong>word</strong> is bold. This <em>word</em> is italic.</p><h3 id="区块标签"><strong>区块标签</strong></h3><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">This is a regular paragraph.</span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">table</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">    &lt;p&gt;This is a p test.&lt;/p&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">    &lt;tr&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">        &lt;td&gt;Foo&lt;/td&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">    &lt;/tr&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">&lt;/table&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">This is another regular paragraph. </span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>This is a regular paragraph.</p><table>    <p>This is a p test.</p>    <tr>        <td>Foo</td>    </tr></table>  This is another regular paragraph.  <h2 id="表格"><strong>表格</strong></h2><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">|列1|列2|列3|</span><br><span class="line">|:---|:---:|---:|</span><br><span class="line">|Header|Title|Name|</span><br><span class="line">|<span class="code">`halo`</span>|[<span class="string">kitor</span>](<span class="link">https://github.com/</span>)|<span class="strong">**ki**</span>|</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><table><thead><tr><th style="text-align:left">列1</th><th style="text-align:center">列2</th><th style="text-align:right">列3</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td style="text-align:left">Header</td><td style="text-align:center">Title</td><td style="text-align:right">Name</td></tr><tr><td style="text-align:left"><code>halo</code></td><td style="text-align:center"><a href="https://github.com/">kitor</a></td><td style="text-align:right"><strong>ki</strong></td></tr></tbody></table></blockquote><h2 id="脚注"><strong>脚注</strong></h2><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Here&#x27;s a simple footnote[^footnote], and here&#x27;s a longer one[^bignote].</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">[<span class="symbol">^footnote</span>]: <span class="link">This is the first footnote.</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">[<span class="symbol">^bignote</span>]: <span class="link">Here&#x27;s one with multiple paragraphs and code.</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>Here’s a simple footnote<sup class="footnote-ref"><a href="#fn1" id="fnref1">[1]</a></sup>, and here’s a longer one<sup class="footnote-ref"><a href="#fn2" id="fnref2">[2]</a></sup>.</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Indent paragraphs to include them in the footnote.</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">`&#123; my code &#125;`</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">Add as many paragraphs as you like.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="删除线"><strong>删除线</strong></h2><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">~~世界是平坦的。~~ 我们现在知道世界是圆的。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><s>世界是平坦的。</s> 我们现在知道世界是圆的。</p><h2 id="任务列表语法"><strong>任务列表语法</strong></h2><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="bullet">-</span> [x] Write the press release</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">-</span> [ ] update the website</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">-</span> [ ] sport</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul class="lvl-0"><li class="lvl-2"><p><input type="checkbox" id="checkbox0" checked="true"><label for="checkbox0">Write the press release</label></p></li><li class="lvl-2"><p><input type="checkbox" id="checkbox1"><label for="checkbox1">update the website</label></p></li><li class="lvl-2"><p><input type="checkbox" id="checkbox2"><label for="checkbox2">sport</label></p></li></ul><h2 id="使用-Emoji-表情"><strong>使用 Emoji 表情</strong></h2><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">去露营了！ :tent: 很快回来。</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">真好笑！ :joy:</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>去露营了！ ⛺ 很快回来。</p><p>真好笑！ 😂</p><h2 id="数学公式-需支持mathjax"><strong>数学公式(需支持mathjax)</strong></h2><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$$</span><br><span class="line">\frac&#123;\partial y&#125;&#123;\partial x&#125; = x + 2\sqrt&#123;a&#125;x </span><br><span class="line">$$</span><br><span class="line">$$\theta=x^2$$</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>$$<br>\frac{\partial y}{\partial x} = x + 2\sqrt{a}x<br>$$<br>$$\theta=x^2$$</p><h2 id="文字样式"><strong>文字样式</strong></h2><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$H<span class="emphasis">_2O$  </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis">$X^2$  </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">mark</span>&gt;</span></span>HighLight Text<span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">mark</span>&gt;</span></span>  </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">font</span> <span class="attr">color</span> = <span class="string">red</span>&gt;</span></span><span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">b</span>&gt;</span></span>Red Color Text<span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">b</span>&gt;</span></span><span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">font</span>&gt;</span></span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>$H_2O$<br>$X^2$<br><mark>HighLight Text</mark><br><font color="red"><b>Red Color Text</b></font></p><h2 id="使用HTML语言嵌入内容">使用HTML语言嵌入内容</h2><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">iframe</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">&quot;//player.bilibili.com/player.html?aid=327623069&amp;bvid=BV1JA411h7Gw&amp;cid=171385214&amp;page=1&quot;</span> <span class="attr">scrolling</span>=<span class="string">&quot;no&quot;</span> <span class="attr">border</span>=<span class="string">&quot;0&quot;</span> <span class="attr">frameborder</span>=<span class="string">&quot;no&quot;</span> <span class="attr">framespacing</span>=<span class="string">&quot;0&quot;</span> <span class="attr">allowfullscreen</span>=<span class="string">&quot;true&quot;</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">iframe</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><iframe src="//player.bilibili.com/player.html?aid=327623069&bvid=BV1JA411h7Gw&cid=171385214&page=1" scrolling="no" border="0" frameborder="no" framespacing="0" allowfullscreen="true"></iframe><hr class="footnotes-sep"><section class="footnotes"><ol class="footnotes-list"><li id="fn1" class="footnote-item"><p>This is the first footnote. <a href="#fnref1" class="footnote-backref">↩︎</a></p></li><li id="fn2" class="footnote-item"><p>Here’s one with multiple paragraphs and code. <a href="#fnref2" class="footnote-backref">↩︎</a></p></li></ol></section>]]></content>
      
      
      
        <tags>
            
            <tag> MarkDown </tag>
            
        </tags>
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
