      <title>MarkDown_Basic02</title>
      <link href="/2022/10/10/MarkDown_Basic02/"/>
      <url>/2022/10/10/MarkDown_Basic02/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><font size="6"><b>This is a series of codes for learning MarkDown Grammar.</b></font></p><h2 id="CodeGrammar"><strong>CodeGrammar</strong></h2><h2 id="代码"><strong>代码</strong></h2><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">At the command prompt,type <span class="code">`nano`</span>.  </span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">`` At the command prompt,type `</span>nano<span class="code">` `</span>`.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>At the command prompt,type <code>nano</code>.<br><code>At the command prompt,type `nano`</code>.</p></blockquote><h3 id="Code-Block"><strong>Code Block</strong></h3><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">html</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">head</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">    &lt;title&gt;Test&lt;/title&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">&lt;/head&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><pre><code>&lt;html&gt;&lt;head&gt;    &lt;title&gt;Test&lt;/title&gt;&lt;/head&gt;</code></pre><p><strong>or <em>fenced code blocks</em>.</strong></p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="code">```json</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">&#123;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">  &quot;firstName&quot;: &quot;John&quot;,</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">  &quot;lastName&quot;: &quot;Smith&quot;,</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">  &quot;age&quot;: 25</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">&#125;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight json"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="punctuation">&#123;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">&quot;firstName&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;John&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">&quot;lastName&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;Smith&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">&quot;age&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="number">25</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="punctuation">&#125;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="Horizontal-Rule"><strong>Horizontal Rule</strong></h2><h2 id="分割线"><strong>分割线</strong></h2><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Try to put a blank line before...</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">...and after a horizontal rule.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>Try to put a blank line before…</p><hr><p>…and after a horizontal rule.</p><h2 id="Link"><strong>Link</strong></h2><h2 id="超链接"><strong>超链接</strong></h2><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">This is a <span class="strong">**<span class="emphasis">*[<span class="string">GitHub</span>](<span class="link">https://github.com/ &quot;GitHub Offical Website&quot;</span>)*</span>**</span> Link.  </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>This is a <em><strong><a href="https://github.com/" title="GitHub Offical Website">GitHub</a></strong></em> Link.</p><h2 id="网址URL"><strong>网址URL</strong></h2><h3 id="针对链接中有空格应该使用-20代替"><strong>针对链接中有空格应该使用%20代替</strong></h3><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="quote">&gt; https://www.baidu.com  </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="quote">&gt; <span class="language-xml">&lt;https://github.com/&gt;</span>  </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="quote">&gt; [<span class="string">ex. link</span>](<span class="link">https://www.example.com/my%20great%20page</span>)  </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="quote">&gt; `https://github.com`</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p><a href="https://www.baidu.com">https://www.baidu.com</a><br><a href="https://github.com/">https://github.com/</a><br><a href="https://www.example.com/my%20great%20page">ex. link</a><br><code>https://github.com</code></p></blockquote><h2 id="应用类型链接"><strong>应用类型链接</strong></h2><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[hobbit-hole] [10010]  </span><br><span class="line">[<span class="symbol">10010</span>]:<span class="link">https://github.com/</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>[hobbit-hole] [10010]<br>[10010]:<a href="https://github.com/">https://github.com/</a></p><h3 id="链接到本地目录节点"><strong>链接到本地目录节点</strong></h3><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Link to [<span class="string">Code Grammar</span>](<span class="link">#Code Grammar</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>Link to <a href="#CodeGrammar">CodeGrammar</a>.</p></blockquote><h2 id="Image"><strong>Image</strong></h2><h2 id="图片"><strong>图片</strong></h2><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">![<span class="string">Markdown</span>](<span class="link">./MarkDown_Basic02/markdown.png &quot;Markdown&quot;</span>) </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p><img src="/2022/10/10/MarkDown_Basic02/markdown.png" alt="Markdown"></p></blockquote><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[<span class="string">![Bilibili</span>](<span class="link">./MarkDown_Basic02/bilibili.png</span>)](<span class="link">https://bilibili.com/</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p><a href="https://bilibili.com/"><img src="/2022/10/10/MarkDown_Basic02/bilibili.png" alt="Bilibili"> “Bilibili Offical Website”</a></p></blockquote><h2 id="转义字符语法"><strong>转义字符语法</strong></h2><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="bullet">-</span> Without the backslash, this would be a bullet in an unordered list.   </span><br><span class="line">\- Without the backslash, this would be a bullet in an unordered list. </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul class="lvl-0"><li class="lvl-2"><p>Without the backslash, this would be a bullet in an unordered list.<br>- Without the backslash, this would be a bullet in an unordered list.</p></li></ul>]]></content>
      
      
      
